keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map jj <Esc>
# I switched these since I am using Tree Style Tabs now,
# so I really want J to move down (=next in the tree view)
# and K to move up (=previous in the tree view). 
map J nextTab
map K previousTab
